        <div class="border-t border-slate-300 pt-4">
          <h3 class="font-lexend text-xl font-bold text-slate-950">Backend platforms</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">APIs, workers, auth, service boundaries, and production recovery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-slate-300 pt-4">
          <h3 class="font-lexend text-xl font-bold text-slate-950">Data infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Query optimization, read-model separation, audit trails, and query routing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-slate-300 pt-4">
          <h3 class="font-lexend text-xl font-bold text-slate-950">Distributed systems</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Event-driven workers, idempotent processing, bounded queues, replay, ordering, and lag visibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-slate-300 pt-4">
          <h3 class="font-lexend text-xl font-bold text-slate-950">Systems components</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Precision-critical components, protocol-adjacent tooling, and latency-sensitive code.</p>
        </div>
